---

## 9. Testing Strategy

**Backend unit tests:**
- `workspace-status.service.test.ts` ÔÇö Test autoProgressStatus with all combinations:
  - Flow state + valid progression Ôćĺ updates
  - Flow state + regression Ôćĺ no-op
  - Sticky state + auto-progress Ôćĺ no-op
  - Sticky state + forced Ôćĺ updates
  - Non-existent workspace Ôćĺ no-op
- Test setWorkspaceStatus always writes regardless of current state

**Integration tests:**
- Archive mutation sets status to `done`
- Unarchive restores `done` Ôćĺ `in-progress`
- PR discovery sets `in-progress` Ôćĺ `in-review`
- PR merge sets `in-review` Ôćĺ `done`
- Manual override from any state to any state

**Frontend:**
- Verify `WORKFLOW_STATUS_CONFIG` covers all `WorkspaceStatus` values
- Mutation hook sends correct payload
- Status icon renders for each status value

