313Ôćĺ// ÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇ Manifest & Task Endpoints ÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇÔöÇ
314Ôćĺ
315Ôćĺ// Get parsed manifest + normalized tasks for a workspace
316Ôćĺapp.get("/workspaces/:id/manifest", withWorkspace, (c) => {
317Ôćĺ  const workspace = c.get("workspace");
318Ôćĺ  const workspacePath = c.get("workspacePath");
319Ôćĺ  if (!workspace.root_path) {
320Ôćĺ    return c.json({ manifest: null, tasks: [] });
321Ôćĺ  }
322Ôćĺ  const manifest = readManifestWithFallback(workspacePath, workspace.root_path);
323Ôćĺ  if (!manifest) return c.json({ manifest: null, tasks: [] });
324Ôćĺ  const tasks = getNormalizedTasks(manifest);
325Ôćĺ  return c.json({ manifest, tasks });
326Ôćĺ});
